@startuml
title Device Service Code Diagram

top to bottom direction

!includeurl https://raw.githubusercontent.com/RicardoNiepel/C4-PlantUML/master/C4_Component.puml

class DeviceApi {
  +create_device()
  +list_devices()
  +get_device(device_id)
  +update_device(device_id)
  +delete_device(device_id)
  +create_command(device_id)
  +list_commands(device_id)
}

class DeviceApplicationService {
  +validate_device_payload(body, partial)
  +create_device(body)
  +update_device(device_id, body)
  +delete_device(device_id)
}

class CommandApplicationService {
  +queue_command(device_id, body)
  +list_commands(device_id)
}

class DeviceRepository {
  +dict devices
  +add(device)
  +get(device_id)
  +list(type, status)
  +update(device)
  +delete(device_id)
}

class CommandRepository {
  +dict commands
  +add(device_id, command)
  +list(device_id)
  +delete_for_device(device_id)
}

class Device {
  +string id
  +string name
  +string type
  +string location
  +string status
  +dict metadata
  +string created_at
  +string updated_at
}

class Command {
  +string id
  +string device_id
  +string command
  +dict payload
  +string status
  +string created_at
}

class DevicesDb <<database>> {
  +engine: PostgreSQL
  +status: planned
}

DeviceApi --> DeviceApplicationService : delegates device requests
DeviceApi --> CommandApplicationService : delegates command requests
DeviceApplicationService --> DeviceRepository : reads/writes devices
CommandApplicationService --> DeviceRepository : validates device exists
CommandApplicationService --> CommandRepository : reads/writes commands
DeviceRepository --> Device : stores
CommandRepository --> Command : stores
DeviceRepository ..> DevicesDb : planned persistence
CommandRepository ..> DevicesDb : planned persistence

@enduml
